for T in range(int(input())):
 n,ind = input().split()
 n = int(n)
 laddu = 0
 for i in range(n):
  ls = list(input().split())
  if len(ls)==2:
   if ls[0] == "CONTEST_WON":
    k = int(ls[1])
    if 20>=k:
     laddu = laddu+(300+(20-k))
     # print(laddu)
    else:
     laddu = 300 + laddu
   elif ls[0] == "BUG_FOUND":
    d = int(ls[1])
    laddu = laddu+d 
    # print(laddu)
  else:
   if ls[0]=="TOP_CONTRIBUTOR":
    laddu = laddu+300
   else:
    laddu = laddu+50
  
 if ind == "INDIAN":
  print(laddu//200)
 else:
  print(laddu//400)
